{"tid":1996863,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】「最靚女主播」丘靜雯又曬比堅尼靚相：夏天真的來了","createTime":"2020-05-01T08:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T07:02:10.000Z","uid":158075,"like":18,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ad82e55c5a453095ba31d7bab1ef3c1e516940c4","tid":1996863,"uid":158075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:53:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/467739/多圖-最靚女主播-丘靜雯又曬比堅尼靚相-夏天真的來了\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F467739%2F%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E6%9C%80%E9%9D%9A%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD-%E4%B8%98%E9%9D%9C%E9%9B%AF%E5%8F%88%E6%9B%AC%E6%AF%94%E5%A0%85%E5%B0%BC%E9%9D%9A%E7%9B%B8-%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=be4a306d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/467739/多圖-最靚女主播-丘靜雯又曬比堅尼靚相-夏天真的來了</a><br />\n<br />\n在now TV任職的丘靜雯（Nicole）有「最靚女主播」之稱，平時她經常在個人IG分享個人靚相，又不時會上載一些做瑜伽的大曬女性曲線。去年她曾分享過一輯比堅尼靚相而引來熱話，更有不少網友到各大討論區貼圖熱議，最近天氣轉熱，Nicole亦隨即發功，分享了兩張穿上泳裝的靚相，並留言謂：「夏天真的來了~今年唔知仲有冇得陽光與海灘呢」，網友都大聲讚好，還有網民打趣留言：「強力建議now 報新聞穿水著（着）」。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DWRqAsg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDWRqAsg.png&h=895b8689&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZdV64kD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZdV64kD.png&h=12359297&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aa087c28d7e93ccf0e41aa146d2edb0578a7e3e","tid":1996863,"uid":3302,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"好想奶爆佢塊閪<br />\n一路奶一路俾佢閪臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef467c9f5b15b56226b5c324fb81ba959489628","tid":1996863,"uid":29929,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"佢又係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6d5655c9c3836d7bfa583ac70c7a28a9afbdcb","tid